{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"87843d8639","title":"中共金华县委关于郑明桂同志右派改正的文件","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"89b0b3f830","index":0,"year":1979,"month":4,"day":15,"articleId":"87843d8639"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3284d51ffe","type":"title","text":"中共金华县委关于郑明桂同志右派改正的文件","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87843d8639"},{"id":"a2bb88f380","type":"subtitle","text":"[郑明桂，浙江金华县寺后王小学教导主任。金惠贤，寺后王小学教师]","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87843d8639"},{"id":"7ec165eefe","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中共中央（1978）55号文件精神和1957年中共中央《关于划分右派份子的标准》的有关规定，经复查，认为郑明桂同志在反右运动中言论，不是右派言论，右派份子属于错划，给予改正，恢复公职和工资待遇。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87843d8639"},{"id":"4b944bb05d","type":"appellation","text":"附：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87843d8639"},{"id":"1f72dd9939","type":"subtitle","text":"金华县公安局文件","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87843d8639"},{"id":"e2474cc55c","type":"subtitle","text":"1979.12.08.","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87843d8639"},{"id":"1a59c0dee7","type":"paragraph","text":"郑明桂同志于1961年1月至3月，为右派份子外流而被拘留审查。经复查认为郑明桂同志为右派外流，在迁送回原籍时拘留审查是不当的。为此经研究决定，宣布给予纠正，恢复名誉。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87843d8639"},{"id":"e8e9d88285","type":"subtitle","text":"中共金华县委关于金惠贤同志受株连失去公职的改正","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87843d8639"},{"id":"af45be5a56","type":"subtitle","text":"1980.07.19","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87843d8639"},{"id":"64a345466f","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中共中央（1979）65号文件精神，经复查认为金惠贤同志确是丈夫郑明桂划为右派受株连失去公职，决定予以改正，恢复公职和工资待遇。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87843d8639"},{"id":"84be96a5e4","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：郑明桂〈魂断婺州〉，载《往事微痕》第35期，2009年11月25日。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87843d8639"}],"page":{"id":"ccf958069b","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87843d8639","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}